data.description: Come Home to Your Peaceful Oasis on Molokai. Go back to a simpler time, and experience home ownership near the water and just outside the charming paniolo (Hawaiian cowboy) town of Kaunakakai. This 3 bedroom 1 bath home with carport offers beach access just across the street where you can enjoy fishing, snorkeling, kayaking, canoeing, paddle boarding. It’s an easy walk to Hotel Molokai with its lovely A beachfront restaurant and bar, boat launch and sandy beach are nearby. Other amenities include a large fully-fenced yard that is great for entertaining, and has a variety of tropical vegetation and fruit, banana trees, papaya, lilikoi. You can sit and sip your favorite beverage while enjoying the spectacular sunsets from the yard or your own living room. Hardwood and tile throughout adds to the cozy atmosphere of this unique property. This is a fantastic, and affordable, opportunity for first time buyers or for investors who are looking for an income producing property.
